          "type": "rule",
          "text": "In your Shooting phase , you can select one unit from your army with this ability as the target of the Grenade Stratagem for 0CP, provided that unit has not already been the target of that Stratagem this phase. This can allow you to use the Grenade Stratagem for a second time this phase.",
